{"tid":1612761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水步黃店被刻意勻難 黑警迫顧客暴曬兩小時致中暑暈到","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:43:58.000Z","uid":34047,"like":24,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"19bc69ae85cf1d16e2f957e6888cb49c5fe4dd55","tid":1612761,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"以後要大力幫襯甜一刻<br />\n再全力抵制藍絲店<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1280250678801418/posts/1343860945773724/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1280250678801418%2Fposts%2F1343860945773724%2F&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a35386ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1280250678801418/posts/1343860945773724/</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載 － 警疑報復搜深水埗甜品店<br />\n三人被捕 一女子暈倒<br />\n<br />\n昨日深水埗福榮街有防暴警察進入甜品店「甜一刻」，約20名市民被防暴警察截查，舉高雙手進行搜身。「甜一刻」曾於早前的深水埗集會派發糖水予示威者。<br />\n<br />\n市民被扣查接近一個半小時，期間有一名被查的女子中暑暈倒，須送院治理。最後有兩名男子被捕。「甜一刻」的老闆亦被便衣警察搜身及搜車，最後被帶上警車離開。<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 壹A傳媒 FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1amedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1amedia%2F&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=be02900c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1amedia/</a>"},{"pid":"17eac86244aac824cacb49ba00819b85fb504e83","tid":1612761,"uid":1550,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"告佢咩？<br />\n非法派糖水？"},{"pid":"788b4552833bcb3d475fc2ef216ef966a5d1043e","tid":1612761,"uid":186142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n係時候推下實際行動 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-l